g.title: Detect.Active->Polling.Active
g.text: Receivers on all unconfigured lanes detected

g.title: Polling.Configuration->Configuration.Linkwidth.Start
g.text: 8 TS2 PAD RX & 16 TS2 PAD TX after 1 TS2 PAD RX

g.title: Configuration.Linkwidth.Start->Loopback.Entry
g.text: If directed | 2x TS1 with loopback bit

g.title: Configuration.Linkwidth.Accept->Detect.Quiet
g.text: 2 ms Timeout | TS1 PAD | No link configurable

g.title: Configuration.Lanenum.Accept->Configuration.Complete
g.text: Consecutive TS2, Link match, Lane match

g.title: Configuration.Lanenum.Wait->Configuration.Lanenum.Accept
g.text: Consecutive TS1 Link, Lane changed | Consecutive TS2

g.title: Configuration.Complete->Configuration.Idle
g.text: TX TS2, RX TS2, Link match, Lane match, DRI match, 16x TX TS2 after that

g.title: Configuration.Idle->L0
g.text: 8x RX Idle, 16x TX Idle after that

g.title: Recovery.RcvrLock->Detect.Quiet
g.text: 24 ms Timeout & No other condition matches

g.title: Recovery.RcvrLock->Configuration.Linkwidth.Start
g.text: 24 ms Timeout & TS Link match, Lane match & changed_speed_recovery = 0b
& ((directed_speed_change = 0b & RX TS speed_change = 0b) | (Current rate = 2.5 GT/s and that is highest advertised rate on TX and RX TS))

g.title: Recovery.RcvrLock->Recovery.Speed
g.text: 24 ms Timeout & changed_speed_recovery = 0, current speed > 2.5 GT/s

g.title: Recovery.RcvrLock->Recovery.RcvrCfg
g.text: 8x TS RX, Link match, Lane match, speed_change = directed_speed_change

g.title: Recovery.RcvrLock->Recovery.RcvrCfg
g.text: 24 ms Timeout & 8x TS RX, Link match, Lane match, speed_change = 1
& Data rate > 2.5 GT/s | 5 GT/s DRI in TX TS1 & in 8x RX TS2

g.title: Recovery.RcvrCfg->Configuration.Linkwidth.Start
g.text: 8x TS1, Link or Lane not match, 16x TS2 sent after 1x RX and (speed_change = 0b | data rate = 2.5 GT/s, no 5 GT/s set in RX TS1 or in TX TS2)

g.title: Recovery.RcvrCfg->Recovery.Speed
g.text: & Data rate > 2.5 GT/s | 5 GT/s DRI in TX TS1 & in 8x RX TS2
& 32 TS2 with speed_change = 1 after RX 1 TS2 with speed_change = 1, no intervening EIEOS

g.title: Recovery.RcvrCfg->Recovery.Speed
g.text: changed_speed_recovery = 1b & EIOS or electrical idle & no TS2 since this state

g.title: Recovery.RcvrCfg->Recovery.Speed
g.text: changed_speed_recovery = 0b & > 2.5 GT/s & EIOS or electrical idle & no TS2 since this state

g.title: Recovery.RcvrCfg->Recovery.Idle
g.text: 8x TS RX, Link match, Lane match, identical DRI
& ((speed_change = 0b in RX | (current DR = 2.5 GT/s and (no 5 GT/s set in 8x RX TS2 ^ ... in 8x TX TS2)))
| 16 TS2 sent after RX one TS2, no intervening EIEOS)

g.title: Recovery.Idle->L0
g.text: 8x RX IDL & 16 TX IDL after that
